      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid, with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken breast</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"><strong>[s]</strong></span> and cook on both sides for 3 min or until lightly browned (don't worry it won't be fully cooked yet!)</p>",
