    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the&nbsp;<strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the&nbsp;<strong>ginger</strong></p>\r\n<p>Dissolve the&nbsp;<strong>chicken stock cube</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"><strong>[s]</strong></span> in 600ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2L]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; this is your&nbsp;<strong>chicken stock&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Re-boil a kettle</p>",
