      "instruction": "<p>Add both the&nbsp;<strong>chopped garlic</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>chopped&nbsp;</strong><strong>ginger&nbsp;</strong>to the pan, reduce the heat to&nbsp;medium and cook for 1 min&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>Shaoxing wine</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>soy sauce&nbsp;</strong>and&nbsp;<strong>chicken stock</strong>, cover with a lid, and cook for 12-15 min until the chicken is cooked</p>",
