    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>wheat&nbsp;noodle nests</strong>&nbsp;with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a&nbsp;separate pot and cover them with&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong>&nbsp;until they're fully submerged</p>\r\n<p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-7 min until tender with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once done, drain and return to the pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (this stops them sticking together)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
