    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, pick the&nbsp;<strong>coriander leaves</strong>&nbsp;from their stems</p>\r\n<p>Trim, then slice the&nbsp;<strong>spring onions</strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>cornflour </strong>to a bowl and gradually stir<strong>&nbsp;</strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong>, then&nbsp;whisk to a smooth paste</p>\r\n<p>Tip: the cornflour and water paste will help thicken your soup!</p>",
