    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the&nbsp;cooked<strong>&nbsp;chicken </strong>from the broth<strong>&nbsp;</strong>to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks &ndash; this technique is known as &lsquo;pulling&rsquo;</p>\r\n<p>Drain the <strong>sweetcorn</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
