      "instruction": "<p>Keep the pan of broth over a high heat and gradually whisk the<strong>&nbsp;cornflour paste</strong>&nbsp;into the <strong>broth </strong>until it's&nbsp;silky smooth and thickened</p>\r\n<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>shredded chicken</strong>&nbsp;back&nbsp;to the broth along with the <strong>sweetcorn</strong> and cook for 2 min or until hot &ndash; this is your <strong>chicken &amp; sweetcorn soup&nbsp;</strong></p>",
