      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>drained noodles</strong> among large bowls and ladle over the <strong>chicken &amp; sweetcorn soup&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Garnish with&nbsp;the <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>coriander leaves </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
